        The National Oceanographic Data Center (NODC) small wave swoosh
                           graphic for decoration
             is one of three NOAA environmental data centers, and
          serves as a national repository and dissemination facility
     for global ocean data.  red arrow pointing right to the NODC overview
                             link NODC Overview

